description:
【代码质量P2】API多个service文件使用 where: any = {} 构建动态查询条件，违反R-01。

问题文件(每个约1处any):
1. services/api/src/modules/journal/journal.service.ts ~line 38: where: any = {}
2. services/api/src/modules/coupon/coupon.service.ts ~line 68,182: data: any, where: any
3. services/api/src/modules/order/order.service.ts ~line 66: where: any = {}
4. services/api/src/modules/notification/notification.service.ts ~line 42: where: any
5. services/api/src/modules/review/review.service.ts ~line 66: where: any = {}
6. services/api/src/modules/trip/trip.service.ts ~line 67,125: where: any, data: any
7. services/api/src/modules/moderation/moderation.service.ts ~line 45: where: any = {}

修复: 将 where: any 改为 Prisma.XxxWhereInput 类型（从 @prisma/client 导入），如:
import { Prisma } from '@prisma/client';
const where: Prisma.OrderWhereInput = {};

铁律: R-01(严禁any类型，必须定义Interface/DTO)
验证: pnpm --filter @zuting/api build
